Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:06.37,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dungeons are places such \Nas abandoned structures,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:08.57,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,fortresses, shrines, or caves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:12.11,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Closed-off areas where battles \Nwith monsters occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:16.23,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Many dungeons are home \Nto low-level monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:21.45,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,while more powerful monsters, like dragons, \Nwill sometimes guard treasures there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:24.92,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,And since you have to work in a limited area,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:27.30,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,fighting them is more difficult than in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.10,0:00:31.57,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, defeating them requires complex teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:10.45,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I know this song...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:17.23,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's the opening theme from \Nwhen {\i0}Elder Tale{\i1} was a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:21.72,Default,Su,0000,0000,0000,,Once girls reach a certain age,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they make their social debut at a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.51,Default,Su,0000,0000,0000,,The ten-day conference that starts tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is also a chance for us to get acquainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:37.13,Title,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1647,1)}The Forest of Lagranda
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:35.03,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,The Forest of Lagranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.20,Default,Su,0000,0000,0000,,Go and join the dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:47.39,Default,Su,0000,0000,0000,,Just look...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:50.11,Default,Su,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is quite interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:51.55,Default,Su,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:54.98,Default,Su,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.53,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I am my lord's ninja...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.86,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I mustn't be seen in such a public setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:04.31,Default,Su,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:06.36,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm better suited for other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.33,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... The obvious choice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.12,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,...Shiroe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:15.98,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,As the Round Table's representative,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to speak with Lord Sergiatte a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:20.34,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Crusty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:25.10,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing this deliberately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:28.59,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose I'll go embarrass myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:33.44,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.74,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,A gentleman must never show \Nhis lack of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:41.70,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you're a member of \Nthe Round Table's delegation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.37,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:45.74,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:49.80,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Then, since you're being a good boy, \NI'll give you a magic present!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:58.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,H-Henrietta...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.54,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:02.65,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Thrust out your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.39,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Put your hand on my hip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:15.52,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I can't dance at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:19.27,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You know what my class is, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:20.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Class?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:22.28,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.53,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I am a bard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:25.70,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:27.53,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:47.08,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,So you are a bard, Miss Isuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.85,HUD1,R,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Isuzu \NRace/ Human \NBard, Lv. 24 \NCrescent Moon Alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.31,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,What an elegant sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.38,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,It perfectly suits this clear night air!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.00,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,You're exaggerating...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:59.24,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what's a bard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:01.48,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,One of the weapon-based offensive classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:07.59,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,But unlike the assassin or swashbuckler, \Nthey play a support role.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:11.00,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Support? Like an enchanter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.37,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:18.02,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,They specialize in lowering enemy stats \Nor enhancing their allies' abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:19.44,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Or so I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:21.51,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,That's a very bland explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:27.40,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The difference between bards and \Nenchanters is that they use music.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:31.89,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,One trait that distinguishes them is the \Nlong duration of many of their abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:35.02,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Think you've got it, Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.33,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Mostly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:40.13,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, it's like any other rhythm game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.35,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Right step.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:43.66,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Right forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:45.36,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Half turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:47.91,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:48.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:50.84,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.28,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Music, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.65,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.26,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.48,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:12.60,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:14.17,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:16.57,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.10,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Play with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.69,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,It's boring hanging around the grown-ups, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.29,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,We're playing hide-and-seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:24.36,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:29.71,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,She disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:30.64,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.74,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,She's a genius at hide-and-seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:37.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:39.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:41.11,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.56,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Can you talk right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:43.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Minori...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:44.63,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:49.36,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, we're going to a dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:52.51,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:07:00.52,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that at your current level, \Nit may be a bit rough...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:05.43,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried I'll slow everyone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.74,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu and the other \Ntrainers won't be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:10.12,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Minori...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:11.89,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:15.66,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And there's more to a battle than your level.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:19.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the basics of \Nparty combat that I taught you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:21.42,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes... Just a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:28.01,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Formation, operator, field monitor... \NAnd patrol teams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.76,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If you remember that, you'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.80,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:33.04,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:38.23,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I know I should understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:42.31,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it's something she \Nhas to figure out for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:44.51,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:50.56,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:51.82,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,This is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:54.94,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,The nobility eats pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:57.08,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,So, the cooking method has spread
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,among the People of the Land...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:05.45,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean we're affecting this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:06.21,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:09.91,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And for us to avoid being \Na destructive influence,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we need to know more about this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:14.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:19.71,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I think I understand what you've been saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.73,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Shiroe,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did you sleep well last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:26.90,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,You had quite a workout!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,One day, I'll get even with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:34.88,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you were the type \Nto hold a grudge, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:37.24,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,How petty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:39.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Akatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You seem a little grouchy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:43.71,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:44.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.17,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.17,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Are, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.00,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.00,SignA,A,0000,0000,0000,,Pear Jam \N{\fs22\c&H496263&\3c&HFBF9F4&}Maihama
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:48.98,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.18,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Pass me the jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:53.67,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right... Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.15,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Michitaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:09.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Did we bring any cooks with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:11.19,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? A few...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:13.61,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We should call in the support squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.23,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:16.36,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:21.37,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,From the size of this terrace, \NI believe they're expecting guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:23.60,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:25.87,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Nobles?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:28.40,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The conference lasts for ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:31.31,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But it isn't held every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:35.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The majority is backroom deals \Nand private meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Like a tea party, you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:40.64,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,The politics here are more complicated \Nthan I'd expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:44.83,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Within Eastal's League of Freedom Cities, \Nthere are twenty-four noble families.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:48.15,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Add in the Round Table, and it's twenty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:53.28,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Sergiatte's city, Maihama, has a \Npopulation of thirty thousand or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:59.81,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That puts Akihabara's strength, with its \Ntwenty thousand, into perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.41,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good idea as to what the nobles seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.57,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Their first goal
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:09.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,was to learn the scope of Akihabara \Nand the Round Table's ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:13.93,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But last night, at the ball, it's likely that \Nwe dispelled some of those concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:18.28,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,So, next, they'll try to win us to their side...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:20.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Apocalypse,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we haven't received any quests from \Nthe People of the Land, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:28.14,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,The May incident caused all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:31.73,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly, the adventurers \Ncall it the Apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:36.79,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, Akihabara adventurers \Nwere merely a disorganized mob.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:39.24,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,That made them easy to deal with individually.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:41.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Exterminating monsters, guarding caravans...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:47.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we paid them, \Nthey were willing to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:52.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But since then, they've stopped coming \Nto our territory almost entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.75,Default,Ki,0000,0000,0000,,And now, they've founded that Round Table,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,trying to rule their city just like we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:01.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard their technology \Nadvances by the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:04.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We must get them on our side, and fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:08.68,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If we screw this up, we could \Nfind ourselves left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:12.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They need our power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:15.48,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But they'll never act like our inferiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:20.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, they'll grant a noble title \Nto Crusty or the Round Table.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:23.07,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Always trying to put us in their debt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:26.20,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is how to deal with them \Nwhen they come to us individually,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rather than through the Round Table.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:29.96,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,It's a difficult problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:35.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, some nobles will try to speak \Nto individuals or to guilds in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:39.59,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,But both the combat and craft \Nguilds are likely to want
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to take them up on their offers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:43.09,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,As will individuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:48.23,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for the Round \NTable to monitor everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:49.60,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,nor is it our purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:53.89,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll have to establish rules of some sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:57.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And that's one reason it's so important \Nfor us to know what they're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:00.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:02.08,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Go and recon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:03.74,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:13.70,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Forest of Lagranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:23.84,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,It's fairly large inside, but basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:27.47,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,at the first branch, the right side \Nleads to the beginner course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:30.35,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,The left is for intermediate players.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:31.98,SignB,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Lagranda Forest \N{\fs20\c&H42559E&}Walkthrough
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:34.15,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourselves too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:38.25,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,It's important to know your own limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:40.61,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, don't get yourselves killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:43.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You'll all be camping in the clearing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,entering the dungeon each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,After you return, I'm in charge of your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:52.42,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All right, time to split into groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:55.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,After that, each group will \Nhold a strategy meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then enter the dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:58.02,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.88,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right, let's start by introducing ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:08.43,HUD1,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Tohya \NRace/ Human \NSamurai, Lv. 29 \NLog Horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:03.52,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tohya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:04.91,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm level 29.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:08.18,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the front rank to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:17.94,HUD1,Se,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Serara \NRace/ Human \NDruid, Lv. 25 \NCrescent Moon Alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.45,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Serara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.48,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a druid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.38,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I'm level 25.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:18.27,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm not good at attacking, \Nleave the healing to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:26.20,HUD1,I,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Isuzu \NRace/ Human \NBard, Lv. 24 \NCrescent Moon Alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.70,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Isuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:21.17,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:23.44,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking part in attacks, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:24.94,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm level 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:26.12,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:32.03,HUD1,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Minori \NRace/ Human \NShrine Priest, Lv. 21 \NLog Horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.01,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.72,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,My class is shrine priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:32.03,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,My specialty is defensive magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:37.35,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I hope to work in combination with \NSerara to keep all of you healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:38.67,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm level...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,21.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:42.99,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,21?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:45.92,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't slow me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:47.93,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:52.11,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Rundel Haus Code.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.81,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Rudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:56.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's your class?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:58.66,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell by looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:00.56,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.55,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You sure talk a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:03.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's your level?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:09.16,HUD1,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Rundel Haus Code \NRace/ Human \NSorcerer, Lv. 23
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.86,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,23... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.83,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's hardly different from Minori's!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:10.57,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Do not fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:14.32,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,My elegant and devastating techniques \Nwill annihilate the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:16.80,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,You can simply stand behind \Nme and provide support.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:19.18,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Your class doesn't fight in front!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:21.21,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry over the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:27.47,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Um, why don't we hold our strategy meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:30.16,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What are we supposed to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:32.14,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I have no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:36.02,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, let's start with our basic formation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.28,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't hard, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:41.48,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Just get yourselves fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.18,0:14:43.11,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:46.15,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:48.48,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to go fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:49.49,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.54,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dungeon, a dungeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:52.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We should be fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:53.98,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:55.74,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Although we must also be elegant and noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:15:00.26,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,But a man must be fired up and hot blooded!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:02.69,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You really do get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:08.63,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get a word in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.63,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya, do you remember \Nwhat you promised me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:19.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:24.87,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,The job of a front-line tank is \Nto absorb all the enemy hits,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:27.03,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,and to trust his companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:28.59,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:30.67,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,as a man, you must promise to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:33.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.02,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:39.97,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with Minori?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.75,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:46.63,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if you ever have a problem, step forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:49.30,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,With your heart, not your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:51.65,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,My heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:53.30,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:09.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:10.65,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:13.96,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! We need some light first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.91,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'll handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.92,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the enemy won't \Nsee it and come for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:22.29,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I hope they'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:23.82,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:27.41,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the enemies here are undead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:28.58,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:31.77,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,The undead can locate us, even in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.68,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,So the darkness acts to their advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:36.01,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Fox Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.18,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Mine is brighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:40.90,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.73,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't the issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:47.22,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,In battle, you're supposed \Nto have multiple lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:51.24,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Then it isn't that my light is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:54.05,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it isn't, since I'm awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:04.59,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:08.74,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like one of the groups that went \Nbefore us fought skeletons here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.46,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,The path splits!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:16.76,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't the right for beginners, \Nand the left for intermediates?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:20.18,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Seems the ones before us went left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,For today, we'll go this way. C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:25.02,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:28.15,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,But don't assume I'll always be turning right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.40,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Rundel Haus...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:37.48,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,You can cast your magic from the back row.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:39.73,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Miss Minori?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:42.16,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,The battle begins the moment \Nthe enemy's in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:47.92,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,I need to minimize the lag between seeing \Nthe enemy and using my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:54.49,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets into trouble, I'll help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:58.75,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't heal as well as Serara, \Nthough we're both healers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:02.72,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,but my magic can cancel a certain \Namount of enemy damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:08.69,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai's strength is its powerful attacks, \Nbut they have a long cool down...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:11.36,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing when to attack is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:12.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:19.82,Monsters,T,0000,0000,0000,,Skeleton                   Skeleton                   Skeleton\NRank/ Normal         Rank/ Normal         Rank/ Normal
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.59,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,There are three.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.55,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.04,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.67,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just charge straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:32.92,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:35.51,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Iizuna Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:40.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai also has ranged attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:42.85,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:44.81,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:47.56,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,He was drawing the enemy's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:50.66,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Whirlwind Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:53.94,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.44,HUD1,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Tohya \NRace/ Human \NSamurai, Lv. 29 \NLog Horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.20,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Purification Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.07,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:04.20,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to use my magic first, or it won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.95,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Heartbeat Healing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:11.25,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya, ten seconds until you're \Nback to full health.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:13.11,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Mister Tohya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:15.38,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:17.80,Default - italics,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Orb of Lava!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:27.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.59,0:19:29.94,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ranged attack, but it's so powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:34.77,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power of the sorcerer, \Nthe magical attack class?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:45.47,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:47.64,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Isuzu, what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:50.33,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I set up a support song in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.45,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,Round Carol...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:56.35,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,If a party member attacks with magic, \Nit automatically follows up with another attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:59.38,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Miss Isuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:04.39,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,My artfully destructive spells have \Nreached the level of legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:06.78,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Grazie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:07.51,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Nice play.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:12.47,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Rundel Haus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:13.16,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:15.32,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Miss Minori?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:18.61,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Have you fallen in love with my beautiful magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:17.98,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,They're targeting you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:26.23,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.45,Monsters,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Skeleton Archer\NRank/ Normal
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:30.08,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,There's another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.71,0:20:31.48,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:33.42,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't checked over there yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:40.28,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Five skeletons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:43.72,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya, fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.68,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, my health's recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.14,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.02,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,They'll attack from multiple directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:51.77,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,At times like these, I must stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:55.97,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,First, I should cast magic \Nto protect the front row.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:21:00.12,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,No... It takes too long to cast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:03.53,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just burn them to ash again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:04.77,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:11.54,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:15.17,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Rundel Haus's aggro exceeded Tohya's!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:22.40,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:24.55,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,My healing magic won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:26.47,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Only one thing left!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:31.69,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:36.33,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,This is pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:40.48,Default,Ru,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:50.45,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your army must be very fortunate \Nto have a commander like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:54.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your strength rivals the Eastern Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:56.08,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,You flatter me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:57.86,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:21:59.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some good alcohol from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:02.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The sun's setting... \NWhy not join me for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,0:22:11.82,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Lord Kiliva...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:14.49,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,But I have another engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:16.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Another engagement?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:19.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Princess Lenessia...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.42,0:22:20.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.64,0:22:23.49,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't interfere with that, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:30.30,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,A pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:33.20,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,I am the adventurer Crusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.77,0:24:08.17,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,The winter rose of Eastal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:10.53,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Long, silvery hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.53,0:24:11.91,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,a delicate curve to her neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.91,0:24:14.51,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,a mysterious light in her blue-gray eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:17.92,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Lenessia El Arte Cowen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.29,0:24:23.14,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Her dream is to lie in bed \Nall day, in her pajamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.48,0:24:30.99,Title,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Shield and Freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.62,0:24:25.55,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Shield and Freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.86,0:24:28.37,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Always look thirty seconds ahead.
